title: The Mad Hatters #33 Sneak Preview: Interdimensional Meth Travel with Jesse Reed
description: Thank you for tuning in for another episode of The Secret Society of the Mad Hatters. This episode Sam and Ryan welcome Interdimensional comedian Jesse Reed and Trans Chaser Trevor Keveloh! We discuss what Jessa has learned after she went on an intense psychedelic meth trip and communicated with beings who are running this simulation. This is life changing! Check out her podcast "The Mormon and the Meth Head!" Available at https://matm.fireside.fm
